            <div class="title">
                Supplies And Services (Transitional Powers) Bill
            </div>

            <div class="right-arrow">
                    <a href="/Commons/1947-08-08/debates/c2847c65-28f2-4efb-8e61-58792b979a85/TerritorialArmyPremises(Tenancies)" class="next" title="Go to the next debate">
