<p class="">I will not pursue that matter further, except to say that the right hon. Member for Woodford would certainly not have been able to maintain his position <span id="1813" class="column-number" data-column-number="1813"></span> as Prime Minister without the support of the Labour Party. I think that is quite clear.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
