                Mr. Osborne
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-0100c76b-f214-4e15-8a17-8936adb22ddc" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
