                Mr. H. D. Hughes  (Wolverhampton, West)
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-dd493bbf-d1b7-4bc7-be36-edc9f1325aaf" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
               data-hop-url-shorten-url="/UrlShortener/ShorternUrl"
               data-hop-popover="http://hansard.parliament.uk/Commons/1947-08-08/debates/457087e1-abae-41e8-9185-76db1506068b/SuppliesAndServices(TransitionalPowers)Bill#contribution-dd493bbf-d1b7-4bc7-be36-edc9f1325aaf">
