<p class="">I will be guided by the Government spokesman on that matter. If I have to choose between guidance from the Government Front Bench or guidance from the Opposition benches, I have no difficulty in making up my mind.</p>                    <div class="hidden-md hidden-lg" style="padding-left: 0px;">
