</div><div class="content-item" id="contribution-689d90c5-b002-449b-953d-9423abc355f6">
    <div class="col-md-9 edit-fail-error">
        <div class="alert alert-danger" id="alert-689d90c5-b002-449b-953d-9423abc355f6">
            <span class="glyphicon glyphicon-info-sign"></span>The edit just sent has not been saved.  The following error was returned:
        </div>
