                Mr. Ede
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-1bdbcff5-9b8a-481c-81cf-6a433d5a3189" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
